{
  "name": "RPlog_Considering_Delede_s_Offer",
  "title": "Considering Delede's Offer",
  "summary": "Aboard the cruiser Audacity near Nar Shaddaa, a troubled Luke Skywalker gathers his trusted comrades, the Horansi Marine Snarl, Ghost Squadron's Chyleni commander Major Kyrin 'Phoenix' Sh'vani, the eager Flight Cadet Doherty, and the XO Kesander 'Sandman' Beysarus, to weigh a dangerous proposition. Colonel Gren Delede of the CSA strike cruiser Authority, betrayed by the Sith Lord Darth Malign and risking his fiancee's life, has offered the Republic an alliance to attack Malign's Imperator-II Star Destroyer, even handing Luke a communicator said to reach Malign directly as a token of good faith. The group debates the risks of trusting a CSA defector, the temptation of toppling the Hutts, and the larger threat the Sith now pose as they break from the Empire. Snarl voices deep skepticism but defers to Luke, and the council agrees to proceed cautiously, gathering intelligence and reinforcements from Falcon Squadron and the fleet before committing.",
